{"title":"Darkness","url":"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/Darkness","type":"markdown","data":"***Obsolete**: This article refers to an aspect of the game which has been removed. It is retained for historical reference only.*\n\n| [![Darkness.png](/images/c/c0/Darkness.png)](/File:Darkness.png) Darkness |                                                                                                              |\n| :------------------------------------------------------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |\n| Level                                                                     | 6                                                                                                            |\n| School1                                                                   | [Hexes](/Hexes \"Hexes\")                                                                                      |\n| Source(s)                                                                 | [Book of Burglary](/Book_of_Burglary \"Book of Burglary\"), [Book of Dreams](/Book_of_Dreams \"Book of Dreams\") |\n| [Casting noise](/Spell_noise \"Spell noise\")                               | 3                                                                                                            |\n| [Spell noise](/Spell_noise \"Spell noise\")                                 | 0                                                                                                            |\n\n|   |                                                                                                                                                                                          |\n| - | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n|   | Dims the light of the dungeon, reducing the range of vision.***“If I must die, I will encounter darkness as a bride, And hug it in my arms.” -William Shakespeare, “Measure for Measure” |\n\n**Darkness** is a level 6 [Hexes](/Hexes \"Hexes\") spell which reduces the [LOS](/LOS \"LOS\") that creatures can see you (and that you can see other creatures) by 25%. Under normal circumstances, this reduces LOS by two tiles. The effect stacks with the [Robe of Night](/Robe_of_Night \"Robe of Night\") and the [demonspawn](/Demonspawn \"Demonspawn\") [nightstalker](/Demonspawn_mutations#Nightstalker \"Demonspawn mutations\") mutation. Higher spell power increases the effect's duration.[\\[1\\]](#cite_note-1)\n\n## Strategy\n\n- Darkness is an excellent spell for situations where you don't want to be seen, obviously. It makes it easier to move into range for [stabbing](/Stabbing \"Stabbing\"), helps when fleeing from monsters at the edge of your LOS, forces ranged enemies to move closer to you, and generally reduces the amount of attention you attract simply by keeping you out of sight.\n\n## History\n\n- Darkness was removed in [0.26](/0.26 \"0.26\").\n- Prior to [0.17](/0.17 \"0.17\"), Darkness was a level 7 spell.\n\n## References\n\n1. [↑](#cite_ref-1) [spl-other.cc:462](https://github.com/crawl/crawl/blob/0.25.0/crawl-ref/source/spl-other.cc#L462) (0.25.0)\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Darkness - CrawlWiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Darkness\",\"wgTitle\":\"Darkness\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":54208,\"wgRevisionId\":54208,\"wgArticleId\":380,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null