t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n\t\t\t<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Darkness</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From CrawlWiki</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\" class=\"mw-jump\">\n\t\t\t\t\tJump to:\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#mw-head\">navigation</a>, \t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#p-search\">search</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"border: 1px solid #f00; background-color: #fcc; border-left: 15px solid #f00; margin-bottom: 20px; width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; line-height: 1.1em; width: auto;\"><i><b>Obsolete</b>: This article refers to an aspect of the game which has been removed. It is retained for historical reference only.</i></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 1.4em; margin-top:0; margin-right:0; padding: 0px; float: right; border:none;\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"border:none; margin:0; padding:0; width:18em;\">\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" style=\"font-size:larger;\"> <a href=\"/File:Darkness.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Darkness.png\" src=\"/images/c/c0/Darkness.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#8195;Darkness\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Level\n</th>\n<td> 6\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> School<sup>1</sup>\n</th>\n<td> <a href=\"/Hexes\" title=\"Hexes\">Hexes</a>\n</td></tr>\n\n\n\n\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> Source(s)\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Book_of_Burglary\" title=\"Book of Burglary\">Book of Burglary</a>,<br /><a href=\"/Book_of_Dreams\" title=\"Book of Dreams\">Book of Dreams</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> <a href=\"/Spell_noise\" title=\"Spell noise\">Casting noise</a>\n</th>\n<td> 3\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> <a href=\"/Spell_noise\" title=\"Spell noise\">Spell noise</a>\n</th>\n<td> 0\n</td></tr>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</table></div>\n<table style=\"background:#f5faff; border:1px solid #cedff2; width:auto; margin: 0px 5%; margin-bottom:1.25em; font-style:italic; text-align:left; color:#000; padding:1.5em 1em;\">\n\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\"> Dims the light of the dungeon, reducing the range of vision.\n<hr />\n<p>“If I must die, I will encounter darkness as a bride,<br />And hug it in my arms.”<br />-William Shakespeare, “Measure for Measure”\n</p>\n</td></tr></table>\n<p><b>Darkness</b> is a level 6 <a href=\"/Hexes\" title=\"Hexes\">Hexes</a> spell which reduces the <a href=\"/LOS\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"LOS\">LOS</a> that creatures can see you (and that you can see other creatures) by 25%. Under normal circumstances, this reduces LOS by two tiles. The effect stacks with the <a href=\"/Robe_of_Night\" title=\"Robe of Night\">Robe of Night</a> and the <a href=\"/Demonspawn\" title=\"Demonspawn\">demonspawn</a> <a href=\"/Demonspawn_mutations#Nightstalker\" title=\"Demonspawn mutations\">nightstalker</a> mutation. Higher spell power increases the effect's duration.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Strategy\">Strategy</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Darkness is an excellent spell for situations where you don't want to be seen, obviously. It makes it easier to move into range for <a href=\"/Stabbing\" title=\"Stabbing\">stabbing</a>, helps when fleeing from monsters at the edge of your LOS, forces ranged enemies to move closer to you, and generally reduces the amount of attention you attract simply by keeping you out of sight.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Darkness was removed in <a href=\"/0.26\" title=\"0.26\">0.26</a>.</li>\n<li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.17\" title=\"0.17\">0.17</a>, Darkness was a level 7 spell.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/crawl/crawl/blob/0.25.0/crawl-ref/source/spl-other.cc#L462\">spl-other.cc:462</a> (0.25.0)</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240916222437\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.068 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.088 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 164/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 795/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1527/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 344/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 5/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nLua time usage: 0.010s\nLua virtual size: 8.14 MB / 50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   65.044      1 -total\n 87.00%   56.588      1 Template:Spell\n 71.24%   46.337      8 Template:If\n  1.95%    1.268      1 Template:Hexes\n  1.91%    1.242      1 Template:Source_ref\n  1.78%    1.155      1 Template:Flavour\n  1.54%    1.001      1 Template:Obsolete\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key crawl_wiki-crawl_:pcache:idhash:380-0!canonical and timestamp 20240916222437 and revision id 54208\n -->\n</div>\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"printfooter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRetrieved from \"<a dir=\"ltr\" href=\"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/index.php?title=Darkness&amp;oldid=54208\">http://crawl.chaosforge.org/index.php?title=Darkness&amp;oldid=54208</a>\"\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"catlinks\" class=\"catlinks\" data-mw=\"interface\"><div id=\"mw-normal-catlinks\" class=\"mw-normal-catlinks\"><a href=\"/Special:Categories\" title=\"Special:Categories\">Categories</a>: <ul><li><a href=\"/Category:Obsolete_articles\" title=\"Category:Ob